item.title: Command Line 101
item.description: This crispy cucumber will have you bashing like a Command Line Hero! Command Line 101 - WebDev, Creating CLI packages, and More (This will be a working doc, as will many of these so excited to see how it turns out!) You know the feeling. The command line cursor is just blinking, staring back at your glazed over eyes as you ponder who in the hell actually remembers any of these commands to use this damned thing.
